Hey all

So, I wanted to share this with all of you, because I think it’s the best idea to honor Stan Lee.

Sign the Petition

In my mind, it’s the best thing to do that will stay respectful of him, instead of using cgi and bad voice acting to make his cameos continue. So if you can sign it and share it around, it’d mean a lot. Not just to me, but to Marvel fans in general.

summary: You know, the only way Infinity War could have been more heart wrenching is if the non-biological parts of those who where...
body:
You know, the only way Infinity War could have been more heart wrenching is if the non-biological parts of those who where snapped were left behind like the clothes of a person or…

- Bucky’s arm

- Falcon’s gear

- T’challa’s suit

- Wanda’s outfit

- Peter’s exoskeleton

- Strange’s cape

- Nick Fury’s eyepatch

I could go on…
